name: The Birds Come to Live in Blockchain

metadata.name: Last Birds of Prey, First Birds on Blockchain
metadata.description:
Millions of animals have been hunted by humans every year. Because of their skin, flesh, or beauty. They are born, open their eyes, And then ... 

Here in the ETH Blockchain, lines appear on a black screen, moving forward and creating living beings. Creatures that were hunted in the real world are now born in the Blockchain World. They have been reborn while still worrying. look at that red circle in the video and realize how it becomes a mist gun in their scared eyes...

"Last Birds of Prey, First Birds on Blockchain" is the first artwork from the collection.

Edition 1 of 1
2500*2500 Pixels
Length: 10 sec
Format: MP4
